{{Quote|I have yet to see a single "gourmet restaurant" that wasn't infested with spacehopping low-lifes out to take my money. When I did finally receive my meal (two hours after I ordered it), it was infested with water lice. Your chef claimed it was seasoning.|[[Zavol Shan]], complaining to [[Ahto Luxury Resorts]]|<ref name="MDoH">{{Wizards|url=default.asp?x=starwars/article/sw20040205manaan|text=Manaan: Depths of History|int=Manaan: Depths of History}}</ref>}}
The '''water louse''' was a species of aquatic [[Parasite/Legends|parasite]] native to the planet [[Manaan/Legends|Manaan]]. Water lice lived in the [[Ocean/Legends|oceans]] where they parasitized many species of [[Fish/Legends|fishes]]. To resist to the parasite, those fishes had developed a [[Symbiosis/Legends|symbiosis]] with [[bakita crab]]s that fed on the lice.<ref name="TOR:VCED">{{TORcite|exp=lots|type=location|Visitor's Center Exploration Dome|Manaan}}</ref>

